Hello peeps you can ask me anything now :o

Anything about me, anything about map making, anything about life, anything about bananas :)

But first here are some stuff that ive built and some montages that ive made :o

Stuff I did in the past
The Original Show Your Face : http://old.avicus.net/forums/topic/783
Dux Hax VI (Texture Pack): http://old.avicus.net/forums/topic/8647 
Da Venum Challenge: http://old.avicus.net/forums/topic/12259
PMC: http://www.planetminecraft.com/member/archeonixx/

Builds/Terraforming
Some Builds leftovers (Mostly Castles): http://old.avicus.net/forums/topic/14857
Some Terraforming leftovers: http://avicus.net/forums/cc03ddad0
Volcano Tutorial: http://avicus.net/forums/439ac2f25

Montages
Nebula Montage #1: "Our Story" https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F7OlUNar-Vk  (Best!)
Nebula Montage #2: "Back to the new"  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uVxIiD_2wao
Nebula Montage #3: "Highlife" https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IR9Su11mQGg

Maps
[Nexus] Archange: http://avicus.net/forums/1151e9d3e
[Nexus] Flare: http://avicus.net/forums/0f83de1f4
[Nexus] The Division 3: http://avicus.net/forums/7969ac2ef
[Nexus] Sandstorm: http://avicus.net/forums/f10c9267c

[Walls] Sandstorm: http://avicus.net/forums/dee5b450c
[Walls] Cataclyst: http://avicus.net/forums/f5f1e6c0b
[Avicade] Frozen Rush: http://avicus.net/forums/8d3ca0bb6


There would be way more maps if I posted each one that I took part into, probably 4-5 more maps...

But I posted those links so you could get come "inspiration"... if you have nothing personnal to ask me, ask me questions on the maps ive built in le past! :D
